 The Transfer Token (TTT) Logo
The Transfer Token (TTT), developed by Atom Solutions Co., Ltd, is a token native to Eternal Wallet, that aims to change the current landscape of currency exchange and overseas remittance. Intended to be as beneficial as possible to its users and holders, it assists in currency exchange. TTT minimizes the costs and fees of exchange compared with the current environment and has a Dividend Distribution. Users are entitled to receive a portion of the fees incurred from other users trading and exchanging on the Eternal Wallet platform, on a weekly basis, in accordance with the amount of TTT they hold in their Eternal Wallet account.
You can download theTTTlogo on full-version of the page.

item.title: TTT
item.description: The Transfer Token (TTT), developed by Atom Solutions Co., Ltd, is a token native to Eternal Wallet, that aims to change the current landscape of currency exchange and overseas remittance. Intended to be as beneficial as possible to its users and holders, it assists in currency exchange. TTT minimizes the costs and fees of exchange compared with the current environment and has a Dividend Distribution. Users are entitled to receive a portion of the fees incurred from other users trading and exchanging on the Eternal Wallet platform, on a weekly basis, in accordance with the amount of TTT they hold in their Eternal Wallet account.
